schools.name: Cobalt Institute Of Math And Science Academy

data.description: Gorgeous two story home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with an amazing open concept that features cathedral ceilings.  The living room and dining room welcome you with two stunning crystal chandeliers, along with a brick fireplace.  The lower level has a half bath and showcases tile flooring.  Upstairs showcases bamboo flooring and features a cozy loft area, two bedrooms, and the master bedroom with a walk in closet and fully upgraded bathroom.  Home has energy saving windows, as well upgraded bathrooms.  The backyard has unlimited possibilities.  Home is conveniently located less than 5 minutes from the 15 freeway, Victorville Mall, shopping, restaurants, schools and parks.
